        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " is the latest Metroidvania offering on the Nintendo Switch. You play as Grey Irma, a warrior seeking the truth behind her life and how it intersects with a mysterious being known as the Sculptor. Grey Irma and many other warriors are what’s known as clayborne warriors, meaning they are effectively spirits that occupy a clay sculpture before moving onto the next sculpture when destroyed. "
